---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="SmartWAN | Cello"
	description="Managed wide-area networking with SD-WAN intelligence, business-only infrastructure and one accountable Cello team."
>
	<section class="page-hero">
		<div class="page-hero-inner narrow">
			<p class="eyebrow">Solutions / SmartWAN</p>
			<h1>Wide-area networking that just works.</h1>
			<p class="lead">
				SmartWAN combines SD-WAN intelligence with Cello's business-only
				infrastructure and commitment to service excellence. One team designs it,
				deploys it and supports it.
			</p>
			<div class="actions">
				<a class="button dark" href="/contact">Talk to our team</a>
				<a class="button dark" href="/digital-resilience">Add resilience</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="section-header">
			<div>
				<p class="eyebrow">The evolution of WAN</p>
				<h2>Built for cloud, SaaS and hybrid work.</h2>
			</div>
			<p class="lead">
				Applications have moved, traffic patterns have changed and visibility gaps
				now matter as much as bandwidth. SmartWAN keeps accountability clear across
				the overlay, underlay and day-to-day operation.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="capability-grid">
			<div class="tile">
				<h3>SD-WAN intelligence</h3>
				<p>Traffic automatically follows the best available path so priority applications keep moving.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="tile">
				<h3>Multi-carrier resilience</h3>
				<p>Multiple circuits reduce single points of failure and keep sites connected.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="tile">
				<h3>Business-only backbone</h3>
				<p>Your traffic runs over Cello infrastructure built for enterprise use, not consumer congestion.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="tile">
				<h3>Service excellence</h3>
				<p>Design, deployment, monitoring and support stay with one accountable Cello team.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="split">
			<div class="ink-panel">
				<p class="eyebrow">Why it matters now</p>
				<p class="quote">
					The network is no longer just how sites connect. It is how critical
					systems perform, how teams detect change and how customers experience the business.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="copy">
				<h2>Connectivity with clearer control around it.</h2>
				<p>
					Cello's future story keeps SmartWAN as a core product, then strengthens it
					with visibility and assurance that help teams understand what is happening
					across distributed environments.
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Prioritise traffic around the applications that matter most.</li>
					<li>Monitor paths and service health before issues become business disruption.</li>
					<li>Support cloud, SaaS and branch environments from one operating model.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta">
		<div>
			<p class="eyebrow">SmartWAN</p>
			<h2>See what reliable WAN looks like.</h2>
			<p>Discuss how Cello can connect sites, users and cloud services with clear accountability.</p>
		</div>
		<a class="button" href="/contact">Get started</a>
	</section>
</Layout>
